        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 mb-8"><div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-red-light rounded-lg border border-red-200"><span class="text-red-brand font-bold flex-shrink-0">!</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Missing Class B extinguishers in aerospace manufacturing facilities with flammable cutting fluids and composite materials</span></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-red-light rounded-lg border border-red-200"><span class="text-red-brand font-bold flex-shrink-0">!</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Expired annual tags in Downtown Mesa Arts Center restaurant and bar district</span></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-red-light rounded-lg border border-red-200"><span class="text-red-brand font-bold flex-shrink-0">!</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Missing Class K coverage in commercial kitchens along Main Street and in the Fiesta District</span></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-red-light rounded-lg border border-red-200"><span class="text-red-brand font-bold flex-shrink-0">!</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Heat-degraded dry chemical agents in extinguishers at Mesa Gateway Airport and nearby industrial facilities</span></div></div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-3 mt-8">Mesa Fire Prevention Contacts</h2>
